#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A containerised version of your external service (not all Dev Services rely on containers, but most do)"
msgstr "外部服务的容器化版本（并非所有开发服务都依赖容器，但大多数依赖容器）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If your extension provides APIs for connecting to an external service, it's a good idea to provide a Dev Service implementation.\n"
"This allows your extension to be used for development and testing in a frictionless way, without the hassle of standing up and configuring external services."
msgstr "如果您的扩展提供用于连接外部服务的 API，那么最好提供一个开发服务实现。这样，您的扩展就能以一种无摩擦的方式用于开发和测试，而无需费心建立和配置外部服务。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
