#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Provide an implementation of `io.quarkus.deployment.builditem.Startable` which knows how to start and stop the service.\n"
"For container-based services, extending `GenericContainer` and implementing `Startable` is the recommended pattern.\n"
"In that case, `GenericContainer` already provides a `start()` method, so the only method that needs to be implemented is `close()` (which can delegate to the superclass)."
msgstr "提供一个 `io.quarkus.deployment.builditem.Startable` 的实现，它知道如何启动和停止服务。对于基于容器的服务，推荐的模式是扩展 `GenericContainer` 并实现 `Startable` 。在这种情况下， `GenericContainer` 已经提供了 `start()` 方法，因此唯一需要实现的方法就是 `close(` `)` （可以委托给超类）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, a minimal `Startable` implementation might look something like this:"
msgstr "例如， `Startable` 的最小实现可能如下所示："

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Waiting for the container to start"
msgstr "等待容器启动"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You should add a `.waitingFor` call to the container, to wait for it to be ready.\n"
"This is typically done in the `configure()` method of the `GenericContainer` subclass.\n"
"For example:"
msgstr "您应该为容器添加 `.waitingFor` 调用，以等待容器准备就绪。这通常是在 `GenericContainer` 子类的 `configure()` 方法中完成的。例如"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Waiting for a port to be open is another option.\n"
"See the link:https://java.testcontainers.org/features/startup_and_waits/[Testcontainers documentation] for a full discussion on wait strategies."
msgstr "另一种方法是等待端口开放。有关等待策略的全面讨论，请参阅 link:https://java.testcontainers.org/features/startup_and_waits/[Testcontainers 文档] 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuring ports"
msgstr "配置端口"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you're extending `GenericContainer`, you should also tell TestContainers what ports to expose.\n"
"This is also typically done in the `configure()` override.\n"
"For example:"
msgstr "如果要扩展 `GenericContainer` ，还应该告诉 TestContainers 要暴露哪些端口。这通常也是在 `configure()` 覆盖中完成的。例如"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, TestContainers will map service ports to random ones on the host.\n"
"In the above code, users can configure a fixed port for the container image, which is then passed to `MyContainer` as a `fixedExposedPort` `OptionalInt`.\n"
"Allowing users to set a fixed port makes it easier to attach external tools to the running container, but increases the risk of port conflicts."
msgstr "默认情况下，TestContainers 会将服务端口映射到主机上的随机端口。在上述代码中，用户可以为容器映像配置一个固定端口，然后将其作为 `fixedExposedPort` `OptionalInt` 传递给 `MyContainer` 。允许用户设置固定端口会让将外部工具附加到运行中的容器变得更容易，但也会增加端口冲突的风险。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Declaring a Build Step"
msgstr "声明构建步骤"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Add a build step that returns a `DevServicesResultBuildItem`, using the `owned()` builder.\n"
"Do *not* call `start()` on the `Startable` – Quarkus will start it at the right time."
msgstr "使用 `owned()` 生成器添加一个可返回 `DevServicesResultBuildItem` 的构建步骤。 *不要* 在 `Startable` 上调用 `start()` - Quarkus 会在适当的时候启动它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With this code, you should be able to see your container starting if you add your extension to a test application and run `quarkus dev`."
msgstr "有了这段代码，将扩展添加到测试应用程序并运行 `quarkus dev` ，就能看到容器启动了。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To allow applications to connect to the service, the build step needs to provide configuration overrides.\n"
"This is done lazily, since the actual service port is usually only known at runtime.\n"
"To configure the port, use `.configProvider(\n"
"Map.of(\"the-config-key-for-the-base-url\",\n"
"s -> \"http://\" + s.getConnectionInfo())`."
msgstr "为了允许应用程序连接到服务，构建步骤需要提供配置重载。由于实际的服务端口通常只有在运行时才会知道，因此这一点可以偷懒地完成。要配置端口，请使用 `.configProvider( Map.of(\"the-config-key-for-the-base-url\", s → \"http://\" + s.getConnectionInfo())` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you need to tell the application where the service is living without using Quarkus configuration,\n"
"you can pass information about the service using\n"
"https://quarkus.io/guides/writing-extensions#injecting-configuration-into-recorders[recorders]."
msgstr "如果需要在不使用 Quarkus 配置的情况下告诉应用程序服务的位置，可以使用 link:https://quarkus.io/guides/writing-extensions#injecting-configuration-into-recorders[记录器] 传递有关服务的信息。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Understanding the builder"
msgstr "了解建设者"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `owned()` builder has several methods.\n"
"Not all are required, but `feature()`, `serviceConfig()`, `startable()`, and `configProvider()` are needed in most cases."
msgstr "`owned()` 创建器有几个方法。并非所有方法都是必需的，但大多数情况下都需要使用 `feature()` 、 `serviceConfig()` 、 `startable()` 和 `configProvider()` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`feature(String)`"
msgstr "`feature(String)`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Identifies the owning feature. Used for identification and lifecycle management."
msgstr "标识拥有的特征。用于识别和生命周期管理。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`serviceName(String)`"
msgstr "`服务名称（字符串）`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the feature provides multiple Dev Services, this distinguishes them. Optional."
msgstr "如果功能提供多种 Dev 服务，则以此区分。可选。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`serviceConfig(Object)`"
msgstr "`服务配置（对象）`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The configuration object for this service. It is compared reflectively to the previous configuration on each restart.\n"
"If the config has changed, the service is restarted; if it is the same, the running service is reused. This controls service reuse, and should be considered carefully."
msgstr "该服务的配置对象。每次重启时，它都会与之前的配置进行对比。如果配置发生变化，服务将被重新启动；如果配置不变，运行中的服务将被重新使用。这将控制服务的重用，因此应慎重考虑。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`startable(Supplier<S>)`"
msgstr "`startable(Supplier<S>)`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A supplier that creates the `Startable` instance. The service is created at build time, but it is not started until the right point during Quarkus startup."
msgstr "创建 `Startable` 实例的供应商。该服务在构建时创建，但直到 Quarkus 启动时才会启动。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`configProvider(Map<String, Function<T, String>>)`"
msgstr "`configProvider(Map<String, Function<T, String>>)`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Provides configuration values that are only known after the service is started, such as mapped ports.\n"
"The key in the map is the config property name; the value is a function that receives the started `Startable` and returns the config value."
msgstr "提供只有在服务启动后才知道的配置值，如映射端口。映射中的键是配置属性名称；值是一个接收已启动的 `Startable` 并返回配置值的函数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For config values that are known at build time, use `config(Map<String, String>)` instead."
msgstr "对于在构建时已知的配置值，请使用 `config(Map<String, String>)` 代替。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`postStartHook(Consumer<T>)`"
msgstr "`postStartHook(Consumer<T>)`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An action to perform after the service starts. Any methods used here will be invoked at runtime, not build time, and will affect startup times. Optional."
msgstr "服务启动后要执行的操作。此处使用的任何方法都将在运行时调用，而不是在构建时调用，并将影响启动时间。可选。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuring the Dev Service"
msgstr "配置开发服务"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To configure the Dev Service launch process, your build step can accept a `ConfigPhase.BUILD_TIME` config class.\n"
"For example,"
msgstr "要配置开发服务启动流程，您的构建步骤可以接受一个 `ConfigPhase.BUILD_TIME` 配置类。例如"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You may wish to use this config to set a fixed port, or set an image name.\n"
"Pass the config object to `serviceConfig()` on the builder so that Quarkus can detect config changes and restart the service when needed."
msgstr "你可能希望使用此配置来设置固定端口，或设置图像名称。将配置对象传递给生成器上的 `serviceConfig()` ，这样 Quarkus 就能检测到配置更改，并在需要时重启服务。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Controlling re-use"
msgstr "控制重复使用"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In dev mode, with live reload, Quarkus may restart frequently.\n"
"By default, this will also restart test containers.\n"
"Quarkus restarts are usually very fast, but containers may take much longer to restart."
msgstr "在开发模式下，通过实时重载，Quarkus 可能会频繁重启。默认情况下，这也会重启测试容器。Quarkus 的重启速度通常很快，但容器的重启时间可能会更长。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Re-use of services between live reloads is handled centrally by Quarkus based on the `serviceConfig()` value.\n"
"If the config object passed to `serviceConfig()` is the same as the previous run (compared reflectively), the running service is reused.\n"
"If it has changed, the service is restarted."
msgstr "Quarkus 会根据 `serviceConfig()` 值集中处理服务在实时重载之间的重用。如果传递给 `serviceConfig()` 的配置对象与上次运行的配置对象相同（通过反射进行比较），运行中的服务将被重新使用。如果配置发生变化，则会重新启动服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is an anti-pattern (and unlikely to work) to use static fields on the processor to store service state or handle service reuse."
msgstr "在处理器上使用静态字段来存储服务状态或处理服务重用是一种反模式（而且不可能奏效）。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/extension-writing-dev-service.adoc
#, fuzzy
